---
title: Chicken & Crispy Prosciutto Caesar Salad with Parmesan & Lemon
description: Ready to give your next Caesar salad a twist? We've got just the dish for you. This Caesar has everything you love about the classic version—cool, refreshing lettuce, creamy dressing, juicy chicken, nutty Parm—except one thing: We've swapped the croutons for prosciutto that you'll crisp up in a pan, then crumble right into your salad for a salty, savory crunch!

